WEBVTT

00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:02.896
The next is universal access
to anti-HIV drugs.

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:04.896
Now, why are these good objectives?

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:06.936
Let's go back to our checklist.

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:10.336
Significant? Check. Concrete? Yes.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:12.176
Action-oriented? Yes.

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.400
Inspirational?

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.880
Well, let's just listen to Bono.

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:18.216
(Video) Bono: So you're passionate?

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.456
How passionate?

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:21.920
What actions does your passion
lead you to do?

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:25.656
If the heart doesn't find
a perfect rhyme with the head,

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:27.896
then your passion means nothing.

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:31.456
The OKR framework cultivates the madness,